// =====================================================================
// System Info (local host metrics) — generated from JSONDB.
// Binding auto-creates channels (memory#, storage#, cpu#, sensors#,
// network#, ...). Only managed link in use: network#ip ->
// LocalComputer_Network_IPAddress (UI item; not in items/*.items — see report).
// =====================================================================

Thing systeminfo:computer:openHABianPi "Local computer" [ interval_high=1, interval_medium=60 ]
